{
  "stem": "1736.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 217.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So what happened was that because my-- the nature of my father's business was a time payment business, I, now, at the age of 12 and 1/2 or whatever it was-- fell on me to go around and do the rounds, which I knew because I had been going with him since a couples of years before that.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I knew all the customers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I knew the lists and that, and now it fell on me to go around and start attempting to collect some of the money that was that was due to us.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course the result was positive in some cases, negative in others-- 'negative' meaning the people that owed us money, if they didn't want to pay, they just slammed the door in my face, or they might just call out some insults and, you know, threaten, don't come back here.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And others were very nice and continued to pay, and it was through that that we were able to-- to buy our groceries, if you like, you know, to-- to live.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, and--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the meantime, I kept on going to Dessau, and then my thirteenth year approached.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, I don't know whether I have this all in-- in the right--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--you know, might be going a little bit backwards and forward.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Time came for my bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, my father wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was nobody in-- in-- I mean, the rabbi had-- was gone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The community was a community made up of a handful of people that were running a-- more or less an underground service.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they arranged a-- a bar mitzvah for me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- do I have to explain what a bar mitzvah is?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was so under--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--under those circumstances.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
